@node Main "Tri_Q - Documentation"

                               'Tri_Q' 2.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Tri_Q' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} played on a triangular board like
this:

                                 o
                                o o
                               o o o
                              o o o o
                             o o . o o

  You play by moving a peg to an empty space, you can only move a
peg two spaces horizontally or diagonally. The game features two
playing mode:

-The @{" Normal " link play} play: you jump over a peg and that peg will be
 removed.

-The @{" Inverted " link play} play: you jump over an empty space and a peg will
 appear there.

  Have fun!

